description: The Compton, Calif. rapper has been in the spotlight all year, first for his beef with Drake, which led to a pop hit and Grammy nominations, all without releasing an album ... until today.
title: Kendrick Lamar releases new album, 'GNX,' capping a year of wins

description: Two big-budget films are set to battle at the box office: Wicked offers a gravity-defying origin story for the Wicked Witch of the West, while Gladiator II revisits the violence of ancient Rome.
title: 'Gladiator II' and 'Wicked' are lavish spectacles — but are they another Barbenheimer?

description: Fans of the Broadway hit Wicked have turned to social media to ask fellow movie-goers not to sing along when the film adaptation hits theaters on Friday, Nov. 22.
title: Fans say, don't sing along when 'Wicked' hits theaters — at least, not yet

description: Susan Stamberg returns with her annual love letter to the pink pile of Thanksgiving mush known as Mama Stamberg's Cranberry Relish.
title: Mama Stamberg's relish faces its toughest critics: NPR staffers

description: Cynthia Erivo says being different had "something to do with" her role as Elphaba in 'Wicked: Part 1.'
title: In 'Wicked: Part I', Cynthia Erivo defies gravity — and convention — as Elphaba
